{
  "eyebrow": "Agent Logic Map",
  "title": "Day 6 · Session + Memory",
  "subtitle": "这张图只讲 Day 6 的三层记忆边界：session JSONL 续聊、system prompt 分层注入、memdir 跨 session 长期记忆。",
  "diagrams": [
    {
      "id": "session-ledger",
      "label": "Session ledger",
      "title": "Session JSONL 如何让 Agent 续聊",
      "summary": "CLI 根据 --resume / -c 决定创建新 Session 还是加载旧 JSONL；run_agent 从 Session.history 恢复 messages，并把每轮新增消息追加回磁盘。",
      "defaultActiveNodeId": "session",
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "cli",
          "kind": "runtime",
          "label": "CLI Runtime",
          "eyebrow": "entry",
          "body": "--resume / -c / fresh",
          "detail": "CLI 解析 prompt、cwd 和 session flag。没有 flag 就新建 session；-c 读取最近一次；--resume 按 id 读取指定 JSONL。",
          "position": { "x": 0, "y": 90 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 0 }
        },
        {
          "id": "session",
          "kind": "data",
          "label": "Session",
          "eyebrow": "ledger",
          "body": "create / load_latest / load_id",
          "detail": "Session 封装 session_id、file_path、history 和 append_messages。Agent Loop 不关心目录怎么组织，只消费这两个读写入口。",
          "position": { "x": 280, "y": 90 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 220, "y": 0 }
        },
        {
          "id": "jsonl",
          "kind": "data",
          "label": "JSONL ledger",
          "eyebrow": ".agent/sessions",
          "body": "{role, content, timestamp}",
          "detail": "一条消息一行 JSON。append-only 的好处是简单稳定：崩溃时最多丢当前回合，不需要重写整个历史文件。",
          "position": { "x": 560, "y": 90 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 180 }
        },
        {
          "id": "messages",
          "kind": "data",
          "label": "messages",
          "eyebrow": "context",
          "body": "restore + append prompt",
          "detail": "恢复会话时，Session.history 先变回 messages；随后当前 user prompt 被追加到内存上下文，也同步写入 JSONL。",
          "position": { "x": 840, "y": 90 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 220, "y": 180 }
        },
        {
          "id": "provider",
          "kind": "model",
          "label": "Provider",
          "eyebrow": "model",
          "body": "complete(messages)",
          "detail": "模型仍然只读取 messages 并返回 tool_use 或 final。会话恢复是 harness 在模型外部完成的。",
          "position": { "x": 840, "y": 300 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 220, "y": 360 }
        },
        {
          "id": "append",
          "kind": "runtime",
          "label": "append_messages",
          "eyebrow": "persist",
          "body": "assistant + tool_result + final",
          "detail": "每轮结束后，harness 把 assistant/tool_result/final 写回 JSONL。下次 -c 看到的是同一份 ledger。",
          "position": { "x": 280, "y": 300 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 0, "y": 360 }
        }
      ],
      "edges": [
        { "id": "cli-session", "source": "cli", "target": "session", "label": "select session" },
        { "id": "session-jsonl", "source": "session", "target": "jsonl", "label": "read/write" },
        { "id": "jsonl-messages", "source": "jsonl", "target": "messages", "label": "history" },
        { "id": "messages-provider", "source": "messages", "target": "provider", "label": "complete" },
