      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "long-term-memory",
      "label": "Long-term memory",
      "title": "memdir 如何跨 session 记住事实",
      "summary": "模型只能提出 memory_write / memory_recall 的 tool_use；真正写 topic 文件、更新索引、扫描召回的是 harness 工具实现。",
