          "label": "topic file",
          "eyebrow": ".agent/memory/user",
          "body": "frontmatter + body",
          "detail": "topic 文件保存完整记忆正文。纯中文 title 会通过 sha1 生成 mem-<hash>.md 这种稳定文件名。",
          "position": { "x": 920, "y": 20 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 220, "y": 180 }
        },
        {
          "id": "index",
          "kind": "data",
          "label": "MEMORY.md",
          "eyebrow": "index",
          "body": "title link + hook",
          "detail": "索引只放短 hook，启动时注入 system prompt。模型看到 hook 后再决定是否调 memory_recall 看正文。",
          "position": { "x": 920, "y": 180 },
          "mobilePosition": { "x": 220, "y": 360 }
        },
        {
          "id": "new-session",
          "kind": "runtime",
          "label": "Fresh session",
          "eyebrow": "no -c",
          "body": "still sees index",
          "detail": "新 session 没有旧 messages，但 build_system_prompt 会读 MEMORY.md，所以模型仍能看到长期记忆索引。",
